    dc:description "Fig. 4. Terrestrial Comorian Hymenophyllaceae. A. Abrodictyum pseudorigidum Bauret & Dubuisson, first identified as A. rigidum (Sw.) Ebihara & Dubuisson, (F. Rakotondrainibe et al. 6771, P 00312031). B. Trichomanes boivinii Bosch, new for the archipelago according to the last inventories (as discussed in text) (F. Rakotondrainibe et al. 6675, P 00311390). Scale bar for both species = 3 cm." ;
